76561198218649903,Recommended,313340,29436103,Posted: 22 January,all,Ghosten,"Mountain is a soothing experience for anyone struggling with anxiety or who just needs a break. To really enjoy what this game has to offer, one needs to have patience and an open mind. Mountain isn't an action-packed, groundbreaking journey; instead, it's a breath of fresh air in our otherwise hectic lives.While the controls are rather self-explanatory, there is a sort of ""piano"" that players can use within the game. The keys for striking up a tune are A-K and Z-M. I don't believe they have any direct effect towards the gameplay, but they're still fun to mess with.Ultimately, this game is perfect for those who need a little time to wind down and get away from everything.-(2/7/17) EDIT: Apparently playing specific tunes with the ""piano"" will initiate certain events! Also, ""."" will ask for the Mountain's thoughts. Thank you @shinymagikarp for letting me know this!"
