,Recommended,313340,31466428,Posted: 30 April,all,Filthy,"Some might say it's a game.Some might say it's a screensaver.Some might say that it's just an idle program.But they're all wrong.This isn't any of those.I'm a bit late to the 'Mountain' Party, but I have learned something while watching my little rock think in space.This is a work of art, disguised as a steam game. It's right before our eyes: the mountain, the weather, the easter eggs, and the thoughts. Your mountain relies on YOU. And if you don't take care of it, it gets depressed.I am not lying when I say that this ""game"" has made me miss a virtual rock, coming to my computer after being AFK for a few hours and thinking ""Oh♥♥♥♥♥♥"" when I read ""Your mountain has died"" along with some unnatural reasoning.This game is a great experience, and I am proud to say that I have gifted it to many friends. More people need to see this amazing experience!Once I was one of those people. ""Oh it's just a stupid idle game.""Boy was I wrong.If you're happy, play this game. If you're sad, play this game. If you're mad, play this game. IF YOU FEEL ANYTHING, PLAY THIS GAME. The ambient noises and PERFECT quality update on 4/20 only make this game better.There are also easter eggs. For example, you can click and drag on items to rearrange them.You can play music with your keyboard.This music also acts as a shield for items when you are dying, and if you play certain patterns, can make it rain unusual things. (Frogs, coins, hearts, etc.)If the music is played in a certain pattern, you will get a window that can tell you the age and weather of your mountain, along with rocks, trees, and plants on your mountain.This game is absolutely beautiful. You are mountain. You are god."
